WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000
NYU Abu Dhabi residential colleges are divided into three buildings, where the floors are separated by gender

00:05.000 --> 00:08.000
There are also designated areas within the residential colleges dedicated to non-visitation community, where individuals of the opposite sex are not permitted entry

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
Each floor has an assigned Resident Assistant (RA) to promote education, health, and safety and community development

00:13.000 --> 00:16.000
Students are assigned either single or double (shared) bedroooms within each dorm

